      "type": "code",
      "language": "csharp",
      "source": "// the keyword in prevents SendCard from\n// assigning to p: p = new Person(...) is disallowed.\nvoid SendCard(in Person p)\n{\n/* \u2026 */\n}\n\n\nPerson p = new Person(\u0022Eleanor\u0022, 22);\nSendCard(p);"
