      "id": "aae821b0-0881-480a-839a-1ce93c4da443",
      "type": "code",
      "language": "csharp",
      "source": "// remember that add was defined earlier\nlet add3 a b c =\n    let sum = add (add a b) c\n    Console.WriteLine(\u0022Result is {0}.\u0022, sum)\n    sum"
    },
    {
      "id": "1b5b49b8-49d0-4332-86ec-604fe4bfc169",
      "type": "markdown",
      "source": "------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n**Exercise 7** Define the following terms in your own words:\n\n1.  Encapsulation\n2.  Referential transparency\n3.  Pure function\n4.  Side-effect\n5.  Mutation\n6.  Immutable\n7.  Binding\n8.  Function"
    },
